...::: Office App Rules :::...
* Check NOTICES everyday before coming to the office
* After entering the office room, first set your IP to the defined country
* Click ENTERED OFFICE after the successful IP setting
* Everyday you must to see at least 40 magics
* Before going home, click GOING HOME

...::: Optional :::...
* You can call/message your colleagues from COLLEAGUES
* You can inform the CEO in advance ( If you need to ) from INFORM CEO
* You can see your profile from PROFILE
* You can logout from LOGOUT
* You can see the updated Office App rules by clicking RULES
